Name: Typing Incremental
About the game: Typing Incremental brings the joys of typing to steam! Have you ever wanted to type out the most used 1,000 words of the English language? What about the top 10,000? Now you can! Type words to earn money, spend money to unlock new words. Complete lists to earn prestige points to make the next list easier!
